Mage pet: 6.1 uptime DPS<br>
<br>
Uptime was 50%.  At L 34, you meditate at 15 mana / tick.<br>
<br>
Assuming you stand while the mob is in camp, that's 5945 mana per caster.<br>
<br>
Wizard damage / mana: 1.89 (+damage shield)<br>
Mage damager / mana: 1.13 (+damage shield)<br>
<br>
Lava storm is a 1.87 ratio nuke (counting earring and spec).<br>
Ice shock is a 2.57 ratio nuke (counting focus and spec).<br>
<br>
So, the wizard could have done a good 15 k damage if he had used ice shock.<br>
<br>
Adding in a horse would have upped damage by another 8 k.<br>
<br>
Adding in a solists wand as well would have upped damage by another 5 k.<br>
<br>
The wizard, with a horse, clarity, and an icy wand, would hit 28 k damage.  Still less than the paladin.<br>
